GM Halts Work at Two Factories in Spain, Germany, WSJ Reports

-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 
2011-03-18T21:27:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/gm-halts-work-at-two-factories-in-spain-germany-wsj-reports.html
  General Motors Co. (GM)  halted work at
two factories in Spain and  Germany  and is considering production
cuts at a facility in  Korea  as it faces shortages stemming from
the earthquake and tsunami in  Japan , the Wall Street Journal
reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
